title: Forager succeeds again
review: Forager is filling in the gap for vegans who miss Kefir.I really like the strawberry flavor.The mango and blackberry flavors have very little taste.I do not prefer blueberry flavor in my foods not pie, tarts, yogurt (I do like blueberries by themselves), so I am unwilling to try that flavor. It is expensive as far as yogurt products go, as is all vegan yogurt.
